'''Sernpidal City''' was the capital city of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Sernpidal/Legends|Sernpidal]]. It was destroyed in [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]], as the [[Praetorite Vong]] used the [[Yo'gand's Core]] tactic, pulling [[Dobido]], one of Sernpidal's [[Moon/Legends|moons]], into the planet. It had a population of 50,000 but its only [[Sernpidal starport|spaceport]] was a fenced-in field.

Sernpidal was the site of [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca's]] [[Destruction of Sernpidal|demise]].

